rComments: Prof Rice has got to be the best prof I have ever had at U of T! Always there for help, very clear and is a tremendous asset to the University.

i entered this class with an abhorrent lack of enthusiasm for latin american politics and left firmly believing rice to be my favourite lecturer at u of t. her excitement was infectious. she was concise with her expectations for assignments and tests, so it was easy to do well
The most annoying thing about this class was the ignorance of the students and the Prof's inability to control it. Very annoying. Best thing? She's a terribly easy marker...for St. George ;)
